<title>USA: Periscope lands AlliedSignal account.</title>
<headline>Periscope lands AlliedSignal account.</headline>
<dateline>MINNEAPOLIS 1997-01-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Periscope, a marketing communications company, said its Communications Alternatives Group was retained to create an advertising campaign and marketing communications program for AlliedSignal Laminate Systems, a unit of AlliedSignal Inc.</p>
<p>It said the account has had capital billings &quot;in the high six figures.&quot;</p>
<p>Advertising for the division formerly was handled by Kamstra Communications, now Bozell Kamstra.</p>
<p>	     ((Chicago newsdesk 312 408-8787))</p>
